## 2) Non-goals (v1 of 3E)
- Full PDF generation engine (optional later; sharing can be basic initially)
- Real-time provider GPS tracking (not needed here)
- Extensive social sharing virality mechanics (keep it premium and minimal)
- Complex dispute workflow redesign (use existing support structures; just integrate)

