## 4) UX / IA Changes

### 4.1 Navigation rename
- Rename customer tab: **Visits → Receipts** (or “History” if you prefer softer language)
- Home preview tile should reference “Receipts” not “Visits.”

### 4.2 Empty-state upgrades (premium even before first job)
When there are no receipts:
- Show a “sample receipt card” skeleton:
  - 2 photo placeholders (before/after)
  - checklist completion preview
  - “Handled standard” badge
- Copy:
  - “After each service, you’ll get a Handled Receipt with photos + checklist proof.”

This prevents the “dead dashboard” feeling.

