## 12) Acceptance Criteria (Must Pass)

### Customer
- Receipts tab renamed and list renders correctly.
- Receipt detail shows:
  - scheduled vs performed level
  - proof photos count vs required
  - checklist completion
  - issues (if any)
- Receipt recommendations (max 2) are relevant and actionable.
- “Update going forward” applies next cycle and updates routine item.
- “Add next time” creates a next-cycle add item.

### Provider/Ops
- Missing proof state is visible and triggers an ops-follow-up path.
- Admin can view receipt and see all evidence and actions.

### System
- Recommendations are deterministic (computed once, saved or reproducible).
- Throttling and suppression rules prevent spam.

